(12, 1, '2020-06-23 11:42:31', '2020-06-23 11:42:31', '<!-- wp:heading {\"textColor\":\"neve-button-color\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-neve-button-color-color has-text-color\"><em>Our Biggest Asset is Our Team</em></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>The foundation of The Kanvan Business is built on a culture of intellectual creatives who value strong character and integrity.</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-normal-font-size\">The Kanvan Business is home to a group of multi creative professionals in four verticals with a shared passion for driving primarily in - <u>Software development, Payrolls, Recruitment &amp; all HR needs of the companies</u>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">Besides these verticals, another vertical is - <strong>Kanvan Sports- formerly known as - STBA </strong>which will provide sports &amp; fitness service to Corporate people on the weekend as if they are part of any sports team, under which they will be keeping themself fit &amp; healthy which they hardly do not maintain due to their hectic daily life routine &amp; desired atmosphere. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">To serve these services in these verticals- we have incorporated our self with multi experienced people from various fields of talent.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customFontSize\":21} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:21px\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customFontSize\":21} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:21px\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About  us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'we-are', '', '', '2020-07-11 06:09:43', '2020-07-11 06:09:43', '', 0, 'http://www.kanvan.in/?page_id=12', 0, 'page', '', 0),
