(32, 1, '2020-06-23 11:48:20', '2020-06-23 11:48:20', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"neve-button-color\",\"customFontSize\":21} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:21px\" class=\"has-text-color has-neve-button-color-color\"><strong><em><u>Software Development, Training &amp; Internship</u></em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customFontSize\":22} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:22px\"><em>Kanvan team helps students &amp; trainees to enhance their skills to the level of market demand by removing some traditional ways which helps them to get a job in their domain without any hustle. Besides these training on Software developing applications, Kanvan also provides internship to IT candidates to explore more on their technology on live projects which helps them to cut off the mark/burden of fresher from their head. They make them self-efficient &amp; independent working people on latest technology which enhances their confidence during further approaches while giving the interviews.<br>Our customers have trusted us for years into Software developing &amp; training programs and given us the confidence to serve them better</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"neve-button-color\",\"customFontSize\":21} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:21px\" class=\"has-text-color has-neve-button-color-color\"><strong>Recruitment &amp; Payrolls (HRMS)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\"><em>Our other talented &amp; experience people also take care of your Recruitment, Payroll, Compliance obligation such as provident fund(PF Employee state insurance (ESI), professional tax(PT), welfare fund(WF).</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"customFontSize\":19} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:19px\"><em>Our operational specialist is also an industry expert who understands all the complexities involve