(181, 1, '2020-07-04 11:50:11', '2020-07-04 11:50:11', '<!-- wp:heading {\"textColor\":\"neve-button-color\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-neve-button-color-color has-text-color\"><em>Our Biggest Asset is Our Team</em> lklkl</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":5} -->\n<h5>The foundation of The Kanvan Business is built on a culture of intellectual creatives who value strong character and integrity.</h5>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>The Kanvan Business is home to a group of multi creative professionals with a shared passion for driving primarily Software development, Payrolls, Recruitment &amp; all HR needs of the companies. We have incorporated our self to offer best services to our clients.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"neve-button-color\",\"customFontSize\":22} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:22px\" class=\"has-text-color has-neve-button-color-color\"><strong>Software Development, Training &amp; Internship</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kanvan team helps students &amp; trainees to enhance their skills to the level of market demand by removing some traditional ways which helps them to get a job in their domain without any hustle. Besides these training on Software developing applications, Kanvan also provides internship to IT candidates to explore more on their technology on live projects which helps them to cut off the mark/burden of fresher from their head.  They make them self  efficient &amp; independent working people on latest technology which enhances their confidence during further approaches while giving the interviews.  <br>Our customers have trusted us for years into Software developing &amp; training programs and given us the confidence to serve them better. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"neve-button-color\",\"customFontSize\":22} -->\n<p style=\"font-size:22px\" class=\"has-text-color has-neve-button-color-color\"><strong>Recruitment &amp; Payrolls (HRMS)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our other talented &amp; experience people also take care of your Recruitment, Payroll, Compliance obligation such as provident fund(PF Employee state insurance (ESI), professional tax(PT), welfare fund(WF).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Our operational specialist is also an industry expert who understands all the complexities involved in the full and final settlement.<br>We manage everything from:-</li><li>Process your payroll based on the latest legislative updates.</li><li>Investment proofs and claims during final settlement &amp; other payment and deductions.</li><li>Provide you consolidated reports</li><li>We ensure day to day maintenance of your arrear register and maintain consolidated arrear computation reports for assistance during audits.</li><li>Provide end to end recruitment solution.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our mission is simple- Making India heaven to work - both employee and employer.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'About  us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-04 11:50:11', '2020-07-04 11:50:11', '', 12, 'http://www.kanvan.in/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
