(250, 1, '2020-07-12 05:00:12', '2020-07-12 05:00:12', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>SDLC (Software development life cycle):</strong>&nbsp;SDLC is a step by step systematic process to develop a software ensuring its quality and correctness. If you are planning to become a software developer you should have knowledge about the proper life cycle of software from requirement analysis to maintenance of the product. There are mainly 7 phases in SDLC.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"type\":\"1\"} -->\n<ol type=\"1\"><li>Requirement gathering and analysis</li><li>Feasibility study</li><li>Design</li><li>Implementation and Coding</li><li>Testing</li><li>Deployment</li><li>Maintenance</li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"neve-button-color\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-medium-font-size has-neve-button-color-color\"><strong>Our team is fully experienced on below technologies &amp; programs:.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>HTML, HTML 5</li><li>CSS</li><li>Java Script</li><li>UI</li><li>UX</li><li>React native Developer</li><li>React JS</li><li>PHP</li><li>Dupler</li><li>Angular</li><li>Python for AI- Artificial Intelligence</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Just for understanding</strong>- The apps developedÂ <strong>with Reactjs</strong>Â rendersÂ <strong>HTML</strong>Â in UI whileÂ <strong>React Native</strong>Â uses JSX for rendering UI, which is nothing butÂ <strong>javascript</strong>.Â <strong>CSS</strong>Â is used for creating styling inÂ <strong>Reactjs</strong>Â while a stylesheet is used for styling inÂ <strong>React Native.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"neve-button-color\",\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-color has-medium-font-size has-neve-button-color-color\"><strong>The 8 latest technologies in software for 2020</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:parag