(409, 1, '2020-08-27 10:55:42', '2020-08-27 10:55:42', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kanvan Business Solutions , is an Indian software development company with headquarters in Noida, India. The organisation focuses on web-based business tools and information technology, including an online office suite, Internet of things management platform, and a Solutions of IT management software. The organisation was founded in 2020 by Bunch of Experinced Folks in Noida, India, and currently holds its presence in different locations and expending the business globally.<strong>SDLC (Software development life cycle):</strong>Â SDLC is a step by step systematic process to develop a software ensuring its quality and correctness. If you are planning to become a software developer you should have knowledge about the proper life cycle of software from requirement analysis to maintenance of the product. There are mainly 7 phases in SDLC.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We provides services in business intelligence and analytics, application development management (ADM), mobility, cloud, social media, testing, enterprise services (ERP and CRM), and infrastructure management services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are Best Web Development Company in India specializes in providing solutions and in designing effective virtual branding and developing W3C standard websites that are compatible with all devices and browsers. We provide best Web Development Services and have been servicing our clients since many years. KBS brings the most satisfactory result for your digital requirements and help your business to grow.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We have dedicated team of experinced developers and designers, creats powerful and engaging web solutios. We use clean and bold design style to provide best standards-based markup code for your web solutions that boast exceptional Search Engine result positions, help increase conversions. As Web And APP Development India, we believe that a good online presence starts with a great web solutions and it goes without saying that the majority of online experiences begin with your web solutions. Your business website and application is not just a virtual representation of your organisation profile. Rather, it mirrors your business objectives and goals. Therefore, developing an attractive, informative, and great web and application solutions happens to be a necessity and not a choice for you. Our experienced team of web developers can do to enhance your results from clicks to sales while keeping functionality and security as top priorities in quick span of time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our Android app, iOS app and cross-platform mobile app developers are update to date in the latest mobile technologies and tools like Android Studio, Xcode, Kotlin, Xamarin, PhoneGap, React Native, etc. to build next-gen mobile applications.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Understand</strong><br>We shape your brands through analytics thinking, applying in-depth research to challenge assumptions at every move.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>WireFrame &amp; Design</strong><br>Our design approach is to simplify. We embrace the joy in creating something unique that is easy for all the users.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Development &amp; Build</strong><br>Using modern technologies, we build with efficiency and skill, creating flexible and scalable business-driven solutions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Deliver &amp; Deployment</strong><br>We take an iterative approach to both our work and our practice, always looking for ways to improve what we do.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Software Development', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '114-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-08-27 10:55:42', '2020-08-27 10:55:42', '', 114, 'http://www.kanvan.in/114-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
